    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >什么是《Iris Odyssey》？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/45707bc708fe68e4d3f63aa89bae6a9a.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/45707bc708fe68e4d3f63aa89bae6a9a.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Iris Odyssey》是一款经典的文字冒险游戏，背景设定在现代的涩谷。故事讲述了寻找哥哥的少女风花和拥有魔法力量的犯罪调查官爱里斯的冒险与心灵交流。游戏中，玩家可以做出选择，这些选择将解锁新的故事情节。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Iris Odyssey》的魅力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/83f86f295647860324cef3523ab8a9f8.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/83f86f295647860324cef3523ab8a9f8.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱里斯与风花，立场迥异的两人，在魔法世界中携手冒险，在不断磨合中建立起深厚情感。请欣赏她们关系日益深化的美丽旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事简回</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/753c062dccadbee5c391f82ee5df0615.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/753c062dccadbee5c391f82ee5df0615.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >居住在涩谷的孤儿少女风花，正在寻找她唯一的家人——失踪的哥哥三叶。在冒险途中，她觉醒了自己隐藏的魔法力量。与此同时，经验丰富的魔法调查官爱里斯正在追踪一个名为“天穹觅者”的犯罪魔法师组织，调查过程中，她对这对看似与该组织有关的兄妹产生了兴趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着风花和爱里斯关系的加深，她们逐渐变得像家人一样亲密。这份纽带是否能足以打破即将到来的阴谋？加入风花和爱里斯，踏上充满命运、阴谋和魔法的现代幻想冒险之旅，开启《Iris Odyssey》的首章！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/66d87057ec033a776a683d3fb9d4fa09.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/66d87057ec033a776a683d3fb9d4fa09.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=601 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/1724f11bfde782ad845579ad89fb2010.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/1724f11bfde782ad845579ad89fb2010.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=601 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/3f337a52639ad7a13ea315c2583aa767.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/3f337a52639ad7a13ea315c2583aa767.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=601 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras/82fdcd6f26f5f66e91a37564cd15abef.avif?t=1771162113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263400/extras_big/82fdcd6f26f5f66e91a37564cd15abef.avif?t=1771162113 width=800 height=601 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日语语音版邀请多位豪华声优倾情加盟！</p>",
